            <dir class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                <div class="about_box">
                  
                    <p>
                        Everybody have dental problems..it can be pain in teeth, inflammed gums, yellow teeth, bad breath,ulcers ,spots in tongue etc.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Taking appointment with the dentist maybe time consuming,costy as well and sometimes you need to see different point of views to check about your case or to know your answer.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Here in DENTAL ADVISOR..we can be your dental consultant….you can save your effort, money, time and most important you will get the advices and medical diagnosis from our highly expert doctors in different specialities in the dental fields.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We will be happy to answer all your dental questions, giving you the correct diagnosis of your case, checking your treatment ,pre and post instructions , providing you with the latest dental tips, general recommendations and advises from

                        our team about your general mouth health as well as your dental condition.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Our staff will be your guide to preserve your oral health, improving your teeth condition,explaining to you the best way to take care of your teeth,gum tongue.


                    </p>
                    <p>
                        You can contact us, send us your<span style="font-weight:bold"> X Ray</span>  or photo of your tooth, mouth ulcer..etc with your question or questions and you will get your answer in <span style="font-weight:bold">24-48 hours.</span> And you can schedule an appointment for zoom meeting with the doctor .


                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We hope that you will be part of our family and patients from US and all over the world .

                    </p>
                </div>
            </dir>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


